Reality TV star and former Big Brother Naija housemate, Tacha Akide has rubbished claims that the show helped her life. Tacha in a short video on her Instagram page on Thursday said the reality show only gave her a platform. She explained that she gave Big Brother a show in return. Tacha also boasted that she was the star of the ‘pepper dem’ season. ”Big Brother gave me a platform and I gave them a show. ”What was pepper dem season without Tacha.? she asked. Tacha was disqualified from BBNaija 2019 edition for violating the rules of the show.